---
// Uso: <TwoCol> con dos <SectionBox> adentro
---
<div class="two-col">
  <slot />
</div>

<style>
  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    margin: 12px 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .two-col {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
